et=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612406\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cnk1665702564805.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cnk1665702564805.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cnk1665702564805.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cnk1665702564805\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                       \n Example: Removing Members\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This example demonstrates how Struct members can be removed (detached) from their parent.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"cnk1665702564805__context_w2503ab1b5b1_w2504ab1b5_w2505ab1\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"cnk1665702564805__note_w2506ab1b5b1b1_w2507ab1b5b1_w2508ab1b5_w2509ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Members are\n            deleted only when there are no more references to the Struct.</div>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">function REMOVE_MEMBER\nvariables\n  struct vStruct\nendvariables\n\n  call printHeader(\"REMOVE_MEMBER\") ; display entry header in the message frame\n\n  ; Build a Struct with two members\n  vStruct-&gt;a = \"AAA\"\n  vStruct-&gt;b = \"BBB\"\n  putmess vStruct-&gt;$dbgstring [<strong class=\"ph b\">1</strong>]\n\n  ; Detach b from its parent:\n  vStruct-&gt;b-&gt;$parent = \"\"     [<strong class=\"ph b\">2</strong>]\n  putmess \"Member 'b' has been removed:\"      \n  putmess vStruct-&gt;$dbgstring\nend ; function REMOVE_MEMBER</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cnk1665702564805__li_d8621e1_d8622e1_d8623e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Display the Struct in the message frame: </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[]\n [a] = \"AAA\"\n [b] = \"BBB\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"cnk1665702564805__li_d8624e1_d8625e1_d8626e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Remove Struct <code class=\"ph codeph\">b</code> by assigning an empty string to its parent. The\n               resulting Struct has only one member: </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">Member 'b' has been removed:\n[]\n [a] = \"AAA\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zva1665702565198.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$parent</a><p>Get or set the parent of the Struct node.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fjy1665702564615.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Adding, Copying, Moving, and Replacing Struct Members</a><p>You can add and replace members in existing Structs, insert them at specified positions, detach them, or move them to new positions, or to new Structs.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612406\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612406\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Example: Removing Members Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Example: Removing Members This example demonstrates how Struct members can be removed (detached) from their parent. Note: Members are deleted only when there are no more references to the Struct. function REMOVE_MEMBER variables struct vStruct endvariables call printHeader(\"REMOVE_MEMBER\") ; display entry header in the message frame ; Build a Struct with two members vStruct->a = \"AAA\" vStruct->b = \"BBB\" putmess vStruct->$dbgstring [ 1 ] ; Detach b from its parent: vStruct->b->$parent = \"\" [ 2 ] putmess \"Member 'b' has been removed:\" putmess vStruct->$dbgstring end ; function REMOVE_MEMBER Copy Display the Struct in the message frame: [] [a] = \"AAA\" [b] = \"BBB\" Copy Remove Struct b by assigning an empty string to its parent. The resulting Struct has only one member: Member 'b' has been removed: [] [a] = \"AAA\" Copy Related Links $parent Get or set the parent of the Struct node. Adding, Copying, Moving, and Replacing Struct Members You can add and replace members in existing Structs, insert them at specified positions, detach them, or move them to new positions, or to new Structs. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}